flowchart TD
    A[Pre-commit Hook Triggers] --> B[Load forbidden-strings.toml]
    B --> C[Walk repo tree]
    C --> D{Forbidden Match Found?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Emit ERR-LINT-### + exit 1]
    D -- No --> F[check-spec-cross-links]
    F --> G[check-tree-health]
    G --> H[check-lockstep]
    H --> I{All Pass?}
    I -- No --> E
    I -- Yes --> J[Allow Commit]
